{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-detail-tsx","path":"/关于css实现div居中问题/","webpackCompilationHash":"3f11ef4d492f86471b0c","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Silence","author":"默尝"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b9a12eb6-f3f6-5c57-a219-e8f6ef0b3a38","excerpt":"Css 实现 Div 居中的常用方法 示例代码 当需要居中的 div 设置了固定宽度 margin  可以理解为一样的意思，如果左右都设置 ，意思就是这个  离左面的距离和右面的距离是一样的,但是此方法只适用于设置了宽度的块级元素。而且当只设置了  或者  或者  时, 也会失效。 原因:arrowlowerleft…","html":"<h1>Css 实现 Div 居中的常用方法</h1>\n<h2>示例代码</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>header<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>nav<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">*</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.header</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.nav</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>当需要居中的 div 设置了固定宽度</h2>\n<h3>margin</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.nav</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 atuo<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">auto</code> 可以理解为一样的意思，如果左右都设置 <code class=\"language-text\">auto</code>，意思就是这个 <code class=\"language-text\">div</code> 离左面的距离和右面的距离是一样的,但是此方法只适用于设置了宽度的块级元素。而且当只设置了 <code class=\"language-text\">position:absolute</code> 或者 <code class=\"language-text\">float</code> 或者 <code class=\"language-text\">display:inline</code> 时,<code class=\"language-text\">margin:0 auto</code> 也会失效。</p>\n<p><strong>原因</strong>:arrow<em>lower</em>left:</p>\n<p>块级元素始终独占一行，无论是否设置了宽度，未设置宽度时他会自动充满，设置了宽度时，虽然他看起来这一行并不都是他的地盘，但是你如果在他后面添加元素的时候，你会发现元素会被挤到下一行去。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>header<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>nav<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  咋回事啊\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a926270c97137f7e12c665232182214d/1b500/pic2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 14.553990610328638%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAIAAAAcOLh5AAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAO0lEQVQI12P4z8CAQMzMIHLXrv9A8OfPf0KA4auz838/v/++viDk7//fyen/+fMgmb9/idD88+d/cgEAxpGdz6of2kQAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pic2\"\n        title=\"pic2\"\n        src=\"/static/a926270c97137f7e12c665232182214d/b9e4f/pic2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a926270c97137f7e12c665232182214d/cf440/pic2.png 148w,\n/static/a926270c97137f7e12c665232182214d/d2d38/pic2.png 295w,\n/static/a926270c97137f7e12c665232182214d/b9e4f/pic2.png 590w,\n/static/a926270c97137f7e12c665232182214d/f9b6a/pic2.png 885w,\n/static/a926270c97137f7e12c665232182214d/1b500/pic2.png 1065w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>怎么肥四，为森么会发生这种情况呢，再看一下面一张图</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/11c57d0a4615876f86f2392f5f0c8a3a/d0baa/pic3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.476547842401501%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAIAAADXZGvcAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAV0lEQVQI12NYXjZzWdmMJcVT5+dNBKK5OROXlkx6s3/2zzNzv52c+/0UTvT15FyGuWUTl9bP3NC5eNfktUC0c9LafTPWfb647e+dHb9u7vh9Cyf6eXM7AOeeWIbv5jUtAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pic3\"\n        title=\"pic3\"\n        src=\"/static/11c57d0a4615876f86f2392f5f0c8a3a/b9e4f/pic3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/11c57d0a4615876f86f2392f5f0c8a3a/cf440/pic3.png 148w,\n/static/11c57d0a4615876f86f2392f5f0c8a3a/d2d38/pic3.png 295w,\n/static/11c57d0a4615876f86f2392f5f0c8a3a/b9e4f/pic3.png 590w,\n/static/11c57d0a4615876f86f2392f5f0c8a3a/f9b6a/pic3.png 885w,\n/static/11c57d0a4615876f86f2392f5f0c8a3a/d0baa/pic3.png 1066w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>可以看到，虽然 <code class=\"language-text\">div</code> 设置了宽度，但是他有一种无形的力量占据了他所在的行的剩下的空间，以至于其它元素无法与其在一行。而这一块橙色区域也就是 <code class=\"language-text\">margin:0 auto</code> 可调控区域，<code class=\"language-text\">auto</code> 会根据这一部分的大小及时分配左右的距离，达到居中的效果，当设置了绝对定位、浮动或将其设置为行内元素的时候，他这种「威慑力」便会消失，<code class=\"language-text\">auto</code> 可分配的区域便会消失</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ae11b0c9cf5e1a1d3af05658aeb7cc22/e486c/pic4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.652296157450795%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAIAAAAcOLh5AAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAXklEQVQI12NYWDBpQf5ECFpYOHlWatfdM9f/////5/fvv4QAw4ryGctKpy0tmQpEy8qmz8/qe3D+FlDzv79//xMCDBWlNTcuX///68+PT19/ffn26/PXv7///CcOAADcJZ97QSgPlgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pic4\"\n        title=\"pic4\"\n        src=\"/static/ae11b0c9cf5e1a1d3af05658aeb7cc22/b9e4f/pic4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ae11b0c9cf5e1a1d3af05658aeb7cc22/cf440/pic4.png 148w,\n/static/ae11b0c9cf5e1a1d3af05658aeb7cc22/d2d38/pic4.png 295w,\n/static/ae11b0c9cf5e1a1d3af05658aeb7cc22/b9e4f/pic4.png 590w,\n/static/ae11b0c9cf5e1a1d3af05658aeb7cc22/f9b6a/pic4.png 885w,\n/static/ae11b0c9cf5e1a1d3af05658aeb7cc22/e486c/pic4.png 1067w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>可以看到，此时那块黄色的区域已经消失，<code class=\"language-text\">margin: 0 atuo</code> 也就失效了</p>\n<p>不过也有一种例外</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.nav</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 atuo<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>此时虽然已经设置绝对定位，div 也已经脱离了标准文档流，但是 <code class=\"language-text\">left:0 right:0</code> 又让其具有了那种「威慑力」，具有了 <code class=\"language-text\">margin:0 auto</code> 可调控的区域</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ab3de802365a2eeb99c694d7b9f6dd4d/943a9/pic5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 10.744580584354383%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAIAAADXZGvcAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAcElEQVQI12P4fXbOrzOzf56e9f3kzG/HZ/69MOvY1EnTknvmZvXOyQQhIGN6Ss+xqZP/nJv17cRMoDI4Ynh8dOnrM2s+XNz45+7uX7d3/3+459b2rTunrN83c8PeGSAEZAC5N7dv/fdgD1DB7zsIBABuoVh7fj02SQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pic5\"\n        title=\"pic5\"\n        src=\"/static/ab3de802365a2eeb99c694d7b9f6dd4d/b9e4f/pic5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ab3de802365a2eeb99c694d7b9f6dd4d/cf440/pic5.png 148w,\n/static/ab3de802365a2eeb99c694d7b9f6dd4d/d2d38/pic5.png 295w,\n/static/ab3de802365a2eeb99c694d7b9f6dd4d/b9e4f/pic5.png 590w,\n/static/ab3de802365a2eeb99c694d7b9f6dd4d/f9b6a/pic5.png 885w,\n/static/ab3de802365a2eeb99c694d7b9f6dd4d/943a9/pic5.png 1061w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>绝对定位</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.nav</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin-left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -150px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>设置绝对定位让其拥有 <code class=\"language-text\">left</code> 属性，然后设定 <code class=\"language-text\">left:50%</code>，但是因为此 div 本身还有宽度，因此还要添加 <code class=\"language-text\">margin-left:-此div宽度的一半px;</code> 让其真正的居中</p>\n<h2>需要居中的 div 没有宽度</h2>\n<p>很多状况下我们要居中的元素是不知道宽度的，有时候可能宽度也不是固定的，因为里面的内容有可能以后要增加，或者随着浏览器的变化此宽度可能也要跟随变化，下面将示例代码的 css 改为如下形式</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.nav</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7c5468f6a401f730531aaf4226bb871d/e486c/pic6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 9.090909090909092%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAIAAADXZGvcAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAFElEQVQI12P4z8BANmL4r61NNgIAcPAukccULfcAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pic6\"\n        title=\"pic6\"\n        src=\"/static/7c5468f6a401f730531aaf4226bb871d/b9e4f/pic6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7c5468f6a401f730531aaf4226bb871d/cf440/pic6.png 148w,\n/static/7c5468f6a401f730531aaf4226bb871d/d2d38/pic6.png 295w,\n/static/7c5468f6a401f730531aaf4226bb871d/b9e4f/pic6.png 590w,\n/static/7c5468f6a401f730531aaf4226bb871d/f9b6a/pic6.png 885w,\n/static/7c5468f6a401f730531aaf4226bb871d/e486c/pic6.png 1067w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>可以看到，当不设置宽度的时候，此 div 默认是充满整个浏览器的，这样的话就无所谓居中或不居中了，通常我们要居中这个 div，是想让这个 div 中的一些信息居中，为了便于演示，我在 html 和 css 中多添加了几行代码</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>header<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>nav<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>热爱前端<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>热爱编程<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>热爱生活<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>渴望知识<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">*</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.header</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.nav</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #fff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">ul</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">list-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">li</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">float</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> left<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin-left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>效果图</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3f56856d6cc35228b10f600b0cec0420/d0baa/pic7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 11.819887429643527%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAIAAADXZGvcAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAARUlEQVQI133GQQrAIAwAwSCkRe3B10WoYPD/b5AtgR5LYRlWSIl6ha2hynHGl0LOiPy0VYV7sNbrGLiHc8aY0ft3Ztv9AYtGNncv4qd7AAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pic7\"\n        title=\"pic7\"\n        src=\"/static/3f56856d6cc35228b10f600b0cec0420/b9e4f/pic7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3f56856d6cc35228b10f600b0cec0420/cf440/pic7.png 148w,\n/static/3f56856d6cc35228b10f600b0cec0420/d2d38/pic7.png 295w,\n/static/3f56856d6cc35228b10f600b0cec0420/b9e4f/pic7.png 590w,\n/static/3f56856d6cc35228b10f600b0cec0420/f9b6a/pic7.png 885w,\n/static/3f56856d6cc35228b10f600b0cec0420/d0baa/pic7.png 1066w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>此时我们应该想办法让 div 的宽度不是充满整个浏览器，让它的宽度仅仅就是里面内容的宽度，这样我们才能让它居中。在块状元素下，如果不设置宽度，它始终是要充满整个宽度的。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.nav</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #fff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inline-block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>当设置 <code class=\"language-text\">nav</code> 为行内元素，或者 <code class=\"language-text\">table</code> 元素的时候他的宽度就默认不是最大化，而是根据包裹的内容改变，也就是最小化。设置为 <code class=\"language-text\">position</code> 或者 <code class=\"language-text\">display:table</code> 也一样。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b05f231210862fb0269f560c2ba12cfb/943a9/pic8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 9.519321394910463%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAIAAADXZGvcAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAASUlEQVQI13XHMQ5AERREUYugeULzfqsgCrF2pVWJyXwW4FT3GugHa6EKLxBBjHAOIWAMkFgLb4a9MyW2xlKYM2u9e3pOHnvz7QevEFs5RC2zJgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pic8\"\n        title=\"pic8\"\n        src=\"/static/b05f231210862fb0269f560c2ba12cfb/b9e4f/pic8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b05f231210862fb0269f560c2ba12cfb/cf440/pic8.png 148w,\n/static/b05f231210862fb0269f560c2ba12cfb/d2d38/pic8.png 295w,\n/static/b05f231210862fb0269f560c2ba12cfb/b9e4f/pic8.png 590w,\n/static/b05f231210862fb0269f560c2ba12cfb/f9b6a/pic8.png 885w,\n/static/b05f231210862fb0269f560c2ba12cfb/943a9/pic8.png 1061w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>text-align:center</h3>\n<p>用 <code class=\"language-text\">text-align:center</code> 实现元素居中，这个属性不是只能让文本居中，它可以让<strong>行内元素居中</strong>，所以只要把要居中的元素设置为行内元素，然向其父元素添加 <code class=\"language-text\">text-align:center</code> ，就可以实现居中</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.header</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-align</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> center<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.nav</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #fff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inline-block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>display:table</h3>\n<p>设置 <code class=\"language-text\">nav</code> 为 <code class=\"language-text\">display:table</code> ,<code class=\"language-text\">nav</code> 就相当与说就具有了 <code class=\"language-text\">table</code> 的属性，那我们都知道 <code class=\"language-text\">table</code> 的宽度是根据其内容的多少而变化的，也就是宽度最小化，而此时 <code class=\"language-text\">nav</code> 便也可以使用 <code class=\"language-text\">margin:0 auto</code> 来居中</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.nav</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">line-height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 70px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #fff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> table<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Css 实现 Div 居中的常用方法","date":"July 18, 2017"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/关于css实现div居中问题/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/谈谈值传递/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"谈谈值传递"}},"next":null}}}